// ============================================
// Shuffle / permute family (Cycle 2301+, Task B-11)
//
// LLVM `shufflevector` requires a compile-time constant mask. The `lane`
// and `shift` arguments MUST be integer literals; passing a runtime variable
// is a codegen error.
//
// Convention:
//   reverse_TxN(v)                 — lanes reversed (v[N-1..0])
//   broadcast_lane_TxN(v, lane)    — splat one lane across all lanes
//   slide_left_TxN(v, shift)       — shift toward lower index, 0-fill high
//   slide_right_TxN(v, shift)      — shift toward higher index, 0-fill low
// ============================================

// --- reverse (single-vector permute) ---
